name: Liquid Finance
public_notice: Water Finance has rebranded to Liquid Finance. Refer to https://liquidfinance.medium.com/wtr-to-liquid-token-swap-597aeccd240d

description.en:
The Liquid Finance protocol combines a combination of DeFi services under one umbrella, with a strong focus on end-users and mass adoption.

The liquid token provides holders with a consistent flow of earning potential. The Liquid token smart contract places a 5% fee on every transaction, whether that’s an exchange transaction such as a buy, sell or sending of tokens. 

We believe that Decentralised finance applications and protocols will be the driving force and growth behind the mass adoption of the cryptocurrency industry.
